snippet.title: Angry Birds Journey | Cave of the Golden Egg
snippet.description:
Red has reached the Cave of The Golden Egg! Amazing adventures with the Angry Birds await you! 

Join the Angry Birds on a magical journey to recover all the Egg Wonders! Fling birds with the slingshot, and topple towers to solve puzzles and rescue adorable Hatchlings in this casual and easygoing slingshot game. Relax and unwind with the most fun and approachable Angry Birds game yet!

😎 Play AB Journey: https://rovio.sng.link/D25fl1/v14y​
